author: Deccan
title: Intex launches new 11000mAh portable power bank | Deccan Chronicle
text:
Deccan Chronicle | September 29, 2015, 17.37 Intex 11000mAh Power Bank is priced at Rs 1,099 for the Indian market. Intex Technologies has announced the launch of its latest portable charger - 11000mAh Power Bank - PB11K, which is available on PayTM, Snapdeal and Amazon. The PB11K has three output USB 2.0 port with different output (5V 1A, 5V2A & 5V 2A). Lightweight charger has a high capacity power with 11000mAh Li-ion Battery and USB cable for charging of power bank and devices.
The power bank device has small power buttons and four LEDs that light up to indicate whatâ€™s remaining. Turns itself ON & OFF automatically, when you plug-in a device. Additionally, the mobile charger consist of torch function that will surely come handy at times of need.
Intex 11000mAh Power Bank is priced at Rs 1,099 for the Indian market.
